---
description: PySpark notebook conventions for Fabric and Databricks
globs: notebooks/**/*,databricks/**/*
alwaysApply: false
---

# Notebooks

- Order: 1_config → 2_setup → 3_cleanup → 4_bronze → 5_silver → 6_gold.
- Always %run ./1_config first; use conf.table_fqn("table_name").
- Parameters: ENV, LAKEHOUSE, MOCK_IPSTACK, LOOKBACK_DAYS, SOURCE_FILE.
- Do not hardcode API keys or lakehouse GUIDs.
